# File-scoped analyzer overrides for `@typespec/http-server-csharp` alpha output.
# Rationale: the alpha emits XML <param> tags inconsistently (e.g. HttpServiceException
# drops `<param name="headers">`), and the emitted surface is regenerated on every
# `nuke Generate`, so fixing upstream once is the only durable resolution. Until the
# alpha ships that fix, silence the emitter-specific doc-coverage diagnostics on the
# Generated subtree only. Hand-written code stays under full XML enforcement.

[**/*.cs]
dotnet_diagnostic.CS1573.severity = none
dotnet_diagnostic.CS1591.severity = none
